iii. describe the relationship between the organization and the assurance provider.

Disclosure 2-6 Activities, value chain and other business relationships
The organization shall:
a. report the sector(s) in which it is active; describe its value chain, including:
i. the organizationÃ¢ÂÂs activities, products, services, and markets served;
